description:
Add method to internal/ticks/client.go to update the awaiting field:

```go
func (c *Client) SetAwaiting(taskID string, awaiting string, note string) error {
    // Update tick awaiting status via tk update
    args := []string{"update", taskID, "--awaiting", awaiting}
    if err := c.runCommand(args...); err != nil {
        return err
    }

    // Add context as note if provided
    if note != "" {
        return c.AddNote(taskID, note)
    }
    return nil
}

func (c *Client) ClearAwaiting(taskID string) error {
    return c.runCommand("update", taskID, "--awaiting=")
}
```

Acceptance criteria:
- [ ] SetAwaiting method implemented
- [ ] ClearAwaiting method implemented  
- [ ] Note is added when provided
- [ ] Method handles errors appropriately
